      "body": "\ufeff## Problem\n\nThe current bundled snapshot is synthetic. It is useful for offline tests, but less useful for showing how PRScout behaves on real repositories.\n\n## Suggested change\n\nAdd one or two small, sanitized real-world examples under `docs/examples/`.\n\nGuidelines:\n\n- Keep files small.\n- Do not include private tokens or personal data.\n- Prefer repositories with clear issue and PR signals.\n- Include a short `sample-report.txt` style output.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n\n- Add example files under `docs/examples/`.\n- Mention the example in `README.md`.\n- Confirm `prscout --snapshot <file>` works.\r\n",
